OL,3,CWorld Cup final 2026: Match underway
OL,4,Cas Spain and Argentina fight to lift
OL,5,Ctrophy
OL,7,FSpain are battling reigning World Cup
OL,8,Fchampions Argentina for the 2026 World
OL,9,FCup at the MetLife Stadium in New
OL,10,FJersey today.
OL,12,FIt marks the end of the biggest World
OL,13,FCup tournament ever, with the final
OL,14,Fwhistle confirming a record 104
OL,15,Fmatches played between 48 teams across
OL,16,Fnearly six weeks in three countries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
