OL,3,CWorld Cup final 2026: Match underway
OL,4,Cas Spain and Argentina fight to lift
OL,5,Ctrophy
OL,7,FThe tournament has delivered thrilling
OL,8,Faction on the field, with upsets,
OL,9,Fdramatic comebacks, spectacular goals
OL,10,Fand standout performances by the
OL,11,Fbiggest stars of the game.
OL,13,FIt also generated plenty of
OL,14,Fcontroversy, from political tensions
OL,15,Fsurrounding the US' treatment of the
OL,16,FIranian team, the annoyance of fans
OL,17,Fover the introduction of hydration
OL,18,Fbreaks and contentious decisions made
OL,19,Fusing VAR.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
