PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784593081
OL,3,CWorld Cup final 2026: Match underway
OL,4,Cas Spain and Argentina fight to lift
OL,5,Ctrophy
OL,7,FNot far from the stadium (temporarily
OL,8,Frenamed New York New Jersey Stadium
OL,9,Fdue to FIFA advertising rules), fans
OL,10,Fhave filled the streets, with Times
OL,11,FSquare becoming a "mini-Buenos Aries"
OL,12,Fas Argentina supporters pack the
OL,13,Ficonic intersection.
OL,15,FTom Cruise, Laura Pausini, Nicole
OL,16,FScherzinger and Robbie Williams were
OL,17,Fpart of a star-studded closing
OL,18,Fceremony, with Jennifer Hudson singing
OL,19,Fthe United States' national anthem.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
