PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784593081
OL,3,CWorld Cup final 2026: Match underway
OL,4,Cas Spain and Argentina fight to lift
OL,5,Ctrophy
OL,7,FAnd in an even more American aspect of
OL,8,Fthis year's tournament, the World
OL,9,FCup's first-ever halftime show will
OL,10,Ffeature Madonna, Shakira, Justin
OL,11,FBieber and BTS.
OL,13,FAnother first ` Not only will the
OL,14,Fwinning side have the privilege of
OL,15,Flifting the World Cup, they will also
OL,16,Fbe presented with diamond encrusted
OL,17,Frings, with 1,996 made available to
OL,18,Ffans to buy for $12,000 (#8,926) per
OL,19,Fpiece.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
