PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784593081
OL,3,CWorld Cup final 2026: Match underway
OL,4,Cas Spain and Argentina fight to lift
OL,5,Ctrophy
OL,7,FSunday's match is the first to be
OL,8,Fattended Donald Trump himself, who was
OL,9,Fpictured in the stadium next to FIFA
OL,10,FPresident Gianni Infantino.
OL,12,FWhen he takes the field Sunday,
OL,13,FArgentina star Lionel Messi, 39, will
OL,14,Fbe the oldest field player to appear
OL,15,Fin a World Cup final, beating Sweden's
OL,16,FGunnar Gren, who was 37 when he played
OL,17,Fagainst Brazil in the 1958 final.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
