PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784593081
OL,3,CWorld Cup final 2026: Match underway
OL,4,Cas Spain and Argentina fight to lift
OL,5,Ctrophy
OL,7,FThe only player older than Messi to
OL,8,Fplay in a final was Italy goalkeeper
OL,9,FDino Zoff ` who was 40 when his club
OL,10,Fbeat West Germany for the 1982 crown.
OL,12,FMessi is also in position to join
OL,13,FBrazil's Cafu as the only person to
OL,14,Fplay in three World Cup men's finals.
OL,15,FAnd since Cafu was a reserve in one of
OL,16,Fhis appearances, Messi would be the
OL,17,Ffirst to start the title game on three
OL,18,Foccasions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
