PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784593081
OL,3,CWorld Cup final 2026: Match underway
OL,4,Cas Spain and Argentina fight to lift
OL,5,Ctrophy
OL,7,FMeanwhile Spain has some particularly
OL,8,Fyoung star talent, with Lamine Yamal
OL,9,Fand Pau Cubarsi, both aged 19, playing
OL,10,FSunday's match.
OL,12,FNo team has ever had more than one
OL,13,Fteen in the lineup and won the title.
OL,15,FArgentina captain Messi says it is
OL,16,F"crazy" to be preparing to face Yamal
OL,17,Fin the final after being photographed
OL,18,Fwith him as a baby.
OL,26,@qD@OrtxD@AOUxD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
