OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784593081
OL,3,CWorld Cup final 2026: Match underway
OL,4,Cas Spain and Argentina fight to lift
OL,5,Ctrophy
OL,7,FThe pair's unlikely connection dates
OL,8,Fback to 2007 when a five-month-old
OL,9,FYamal was held by Messi after his
OL,10,Fparents won a charity photoshoot in
OL,11,FBarcelona.
OL,13,FSpain is 28-0-9 in its last 37
OL,14,Fmatches, which has tied Italy for the
OL,15,Flongest unbeaten run by a European
OL,16,Fmen's national team.
OL,18,FItaly also went 28-0-9 from October
OL,19,F2018 through September 2021 ` before
OL,20,Flosing to Spain 2-1 on Oct. 6, 2021 in
OL,21,FMilan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
