OL,3,CWorld Cup final 2026: Match underway
OL,4,Cas Spain and Argentina fight to lift
OL,5,Ctrophy
OL,7,FAcross all competitions and
OL,8,Ffriendlies, the sides have played 14
OL,9,Ftimes. Each has won six times and they
OL,10,Ftied twice.
OL,12,FWhat time is kick-off and where can I
OL,13,Fwatch the final?
OL,15,FSpain and Argentina will kick-off at
OL,16,F8pm BST at the New York New Jersey
OL,17,FStadium.
OL,19,FYou can watch the match on ITV1 or on
OL,20,FSTV, with pre-match coverage starting
OL,21,Fat 8.45pm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
